column5: A beautiful summer day on the first day of autumn.
Closed the pool for the season yesterday... I enjoyed that! HH
I painted all day inside so I couldn't have cared less what the day was like.
I liked the weather so much I feel a sick day Comming for tommorow !!!!! This is our Indian summer for sure !!!!! I hear brown & green fish calling my name !!!!! Fish-on .....woo hoo
